Package: oFDAinfo
Title: Pulls Data From The FDA openAPI
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jonah",
           family = "Gorodensky",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jonahgoro@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: oFDAinfo pulls data from the FDA's openAPI. The package allows users to specify drugs of interest, and the data available will be collated and output as a dataframe (and a saved to a file if desired). As of now the functions only work on NDC type queries within the FDA.
